Package: mcMDISolver
Type: Package
Title: Monte Carlo Minimum Discrimination Information Solver
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Imports:
    nleqslv,
    parallel
Authors@R: person("Miguel", "Biron", email = "miguelbl9@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements a Monte Carlo approach to solving Minimum
    Discrimination Information (also called Minimum Cross - Entropy) with linear
    constraints for arbitrary distributions in $\mathbb{R}^n$. Parallel implementation
    is provided for faster computations.
License: GPL-3
